        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2180360031" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14284632828729914001">I LOVE this book! It was an impulse buy when I ran into the author in the mall around 1 AM on Black Friday, and that was a decision I will never forget or regret! <br/>My favorite thing about this book is how true to character it stays. Vampire and LDS are not two cultures I ever expected to be combined in a story, but the actions and reactions play out so beautifully, it feels like how things would ACTUALLY happen if the circumstances were to arise.</span>

          </span>
